Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过还有别的生活方式\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You said there were other ways to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-没错  -比如说什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}That's right. - Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道我看到了什么吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You know what I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到的是一群不好惹的陆战队员\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I see some hard- ass Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这间屋子里没有看到失败\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I do not see defeat in this room,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有看到投降\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and I do not see surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,敌军就在门口了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The enemy is at our gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,数量碾压我们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Their numbers are overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,抵挡得了一时 抵挡不了一世\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We will not be able to hold them back forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就让致远星沦陷吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Just let Reach fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道会发生这样的事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They knew this was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们早就预见到这种结果 于是做了权衡\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They saw it coming, they did the math.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么时候离开海军情报局的 上将\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}When did you leave ONI, Admiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你从没离开\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You never left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥部撤退了 高级人员也跟着走了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Command bugged out. Took high- ranking personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还带走了高价值资产\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Valuable assets.
