Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,达尼洛在哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's Danilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他阵亡了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们站在一起的所有陆战队员\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Any Marine who makes this stand with us. ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都难逃一死\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}...will not survive the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有火吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Got a light? -
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们多拖住\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}For every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人一刻\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}that we hold the enemy at bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就能有更多的无辜平民登上运输飞船逃离\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}more innocent people can escape on the transports.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们安全离开后\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And when they do,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,会向外讲述\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}they will go forth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们今天谱写的故事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and tell the story that you write today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们将会被铭记\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You will be remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是勇敢的女性和男性\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}...as the brave women and men
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,牺牲了自己的生命\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}who laid down their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们的孩子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}so that our children
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,无需生活在\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}may live without fear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,战争怪物的阴影下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}of this monster we call war.
