Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切还没有结束\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Look at them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们回来了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They're coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,目标视野良好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Target in the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就这点本事吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Is that all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想着我不该说话 但我还是说了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I thought I shouldn't have said anything, but I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在我后悔说话了  -别说话了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Now I regret saying it. - Please stop talking.
