Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,草 啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, shit! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是我干 那是我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I did that. That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这事肯定是没完没了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm never gonna hear the end of this.
