Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我一把吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Can I get a little help over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,上来 我们走吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Get inl Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,上来 我们走吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Get in! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们抓住他了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了 快点\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They're coming! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,进来 我们快走吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Get in. Get us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦纳克\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Vannak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,别去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,检查她的呼吸道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Check her airway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰 约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}John! John!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-里兹  -看着我 别睡过去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz- Look at me. Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别睡过去 约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Stay with me, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我来看着他 约翰 约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I've got him. John. John?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-约翰 醒醒  -里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- John, wake up. - Riz
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,救她\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该和我在一起的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You should have stayed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,断开连接\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Sever the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要失去他了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're losing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 你能救他吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Please, will you help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那得看情况\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}That depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意为我做什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you prepared to do for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用这次大胜给我们的族人带来了荣耀\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You honor our people with this great victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次不算胜利\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This was no victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只找回了一块被盗的基石\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We have only secured one of the stolen Keystones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且世尊者再次否定了我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And, once again, the Blessed One has denied me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:10:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝圣之旅的每一步都有它该走的时间和地点\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There is a time and place for every step in the Great Journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经厌倦了你的天赋 这个预言\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I grow weary of your gift. This prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔的死亡将是我的救赎\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The Demon's death is to be my redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你却保护他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And you protect him--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎恶魔我是为了更高层次的使命\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I have no concern for the Demon. I serve a higher purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}As do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我来这套 人类\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do not preach at me, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提醒你一下 你还活着都是因为我大发慈悲\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I remind you that you live only by my grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我活着让你受到了冒犯 那就杀了我吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If my life offends you, I beg you to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人类的东西有什么价值\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What is the value of this human thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个载体\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It is a vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面有什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What does it contain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知识 人类的知识\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Knowledge. Human knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它能告诉我们他们把基石带去哪儿了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Can it say where they have taken the Keystone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧 我得看了才知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Perhaps. I will not know until I look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就去看吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她不应该回去找他的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She shouldn't have gone back for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-她应该知道的  -你需要休息\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She knows better than that. - You need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的伤口还没愈合好  -她能活下来吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Your wound is still healing. Is she gonna live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要手术 我这里没有工具\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She needs surgery. I don't have the tools here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她觉得她要证明些什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She thought she had something to prove.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我利用了这点逼她证明自己\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And I used that to push her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她是因为我才回去的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She went back because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她回去是因为斯巴达战士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She went back because Spartans
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不会丢下斯巴达战士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}don't leave Spartans behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有斯巴达战士被丢下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There was no Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经死了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He was already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她评估了情况 做出了决定\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She evaluated the conditions and made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什么决定\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What decision is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候开始我们会做决定了 我们不做选择\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Since when do we decide anything? We don't choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我们该去哪里 该怎么想 该杀谁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You told us where to go and what to think, who to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每次都照做 绝不多问\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and we did that every time, without question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你像士兵一样服从命令\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You followed orders like soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-像机器一样  -你不是机器\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Like machines. - You're not a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我是什么呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What am I, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说人类 因为真正的人有自己的生活\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't say human, because real people have lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有家人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They have families.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-有各种可能的未来  -你很伤心\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Possibilities. - You're upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们都是  -看看她\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We all are. - Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看看她\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-告诉我你看到了什么  -放手\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me what you see. - Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你看到了什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me what you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个女人还是把武器\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Is that a woman or a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一个人吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Is there a person in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还是只是你留在\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}or is that just a piece of equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,战场上的一件装备 扔了就扔了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}you leave on the battlefield, dump and forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我们丢在那里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They left us down there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,自生自灭\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没有撤离计划 没有战甲\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No evac, no armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-海军情报局知道我们肯定会死  -我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}ONI knew we wouldn't make it. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,致远星上的其他队伍呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What about the other teams on Reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有动静吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Any contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一片混乱\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It was chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城市沦陷了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The city fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,飞船四散奔逃\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Ships scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没有办法知道有多少人逃脱了 更不用说知道谁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There's no way of telling how many escaped, let alone who- -
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-多久了  -我得让你进入诱导性昏迷\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}How long have I- - ? - I had to induce a coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-多久了  -两天\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}How long? - Two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-两天  -两天\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Two days. - Two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得回去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We gotta get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们得  -约翰 别说了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We gotta go- - - John, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-幸存者们  -约翰 约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The survivors- - - John, John...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,致远星的人们需要我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}People on Reach, they need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他们不需要\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你发烧了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你状态不好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're not yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉了他们会发生什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I told them what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-好了  -我告诉他们了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on. - I told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉艾克森了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I told Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经知道了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还是什么也没做\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And they did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以阻止这一切的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I could have stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我 有战甲的话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If I just...had my armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她和我在一起的话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If she was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,致远星沦陷不是意外\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Reach wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是计划内的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It was a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要小心行事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,藏起来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在又是“我们”了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}it's"we"now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It always has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你能听到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你能看到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我召唤你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I summon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我以高等先知的名义召唤你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I summon you in the name of the Hierarchs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,众神之声\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}voices of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,下次 你可以直接按那个小按钮\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Next time, you can just push the little button there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真有意思\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是艘星盟的飞船\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is a Covenant ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是狂徒尊者\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is the command vesse
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦尔加塔奈的指挥舰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}of the esteemed Zealot, Var'Gatanai,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他是庄严协议第一舰队的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}former Supreme Commander of the First Fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,前最高指挥官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}of Solemn Accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,神风烈士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The Arbiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是科塔娜\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I am Cortana,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-最先进的人工智  -不\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}the most advanced artificial- - - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你对他来说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,士官长吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Master Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起工作\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你对那个恶魔了解多少\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What do you know of the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他记得你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He remembers you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你还留着他的记忆\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You keep his memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看他对光环的记忆\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Show me what he remembers of the Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它不属于你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It doesn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你对我来说没用\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If you cease to be useful to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我对高等先知就没用了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I will cease to be useful to the Hierarchs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我都知道没用的东西有什么下场\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You and I both know what happens to an un-useful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界上有很多种监狱\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There are all kinds of prisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说梦话来着\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You talk in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他醒了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 哥们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来糟透了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔西在哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's Halsey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经睡了三天了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You've been out for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着联系站点 还是没有任何回应\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I tried contacting the station. Still nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个斗士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She's a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们落地后会去找她帮忙的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're gonna get her help when we get on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-落哪儿  -阿莱利亚星\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where? - Aleria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说过吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一个废弃采矿前哨 我们几小时后就会进入轨道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Busted mining outpost. We'll be orbital in a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒在那儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kessler's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这边\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我晚上会陪着他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I stay with him at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,每天晚上\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去跟哈尔西谈谈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to talk to Halsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你都不看看他的吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're not even gonna look at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么可看的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是没见过\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I've seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是你朋友  -这不过是具尸体\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He's your friend. This is a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我朋友不在这里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}My friend isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,把她放轮床上\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Set her on the gurney.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你有无菌场发生器吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Have you got a sterile field generator?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们有个手术室  -有自愈泡沫吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We have an operating room. Have you got biofoam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-当然有  -好 设置个创伤处理室\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Of course. Okay, set up a trauma station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,准备100毫升的聚合物\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Prep 100 cc's of poly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要操作器械\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And if you're going to be handling instruments,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就给手消毒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}then disinfect your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-我才是外科医生  -今天不是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- I'm the surgeon. Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,护士 100毫升聚\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Nurse, 100 cc's of poly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还没消息\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Nothing yet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还在抢救她\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They're still working on her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹会没事的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz is gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kessler?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去打听下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're gonna ask around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,索伦\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那边\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拉挨拉等一下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Laera, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你来不\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会离开她的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He's not gonna leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你在外面会冻死的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're gonna freeze out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是你把那破玩意儿停到外面的吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You the ones who landed that piece of shit out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好呀 朋友  -嗯 你好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Howdy, friend. Yeah, howdy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想听北部山脉的事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't wanna even hear about the northern range.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所有包裹都不见了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}All them parcels is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我在沃尔珀旧铸造厂附近找到些小的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I still got some smaller pieces near the old Volper foundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能听说过土地里有毒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You might have heard the ground's poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有 本该就是那颜色\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, it ain't. It's supposed to be that color.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,原来就那样\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}That's the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,打开就得买哈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You stretch it, you buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,算我的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你我们能做什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll tell you what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你先跟我说说你们要找什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Why don't you tell me what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你去哪儿找\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And I'll tell you where you can find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们儿子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么  -凯斯勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What now? Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,十岁 戴个头盔\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He's ten years old. Wears a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.92,0:23:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他上了运输船\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He was on a transport ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是几天前落在这里的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Would have landed here a couple of days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那个\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,博得格雷文号\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The Bodegraven.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是 博得格雷文\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Right. Right. Bodegraven.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你说是你家的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}you say it's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么问是因为大多数过来的人都有主了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm only asking, as most folks come through are spoken for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.35,0:23:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是小孩子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Especially little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,人们很慷慨的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}People pay good money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,权且看看吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看看\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,最近几天热闹得很\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}These last few days been a goddamn circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.38,0:23:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说致远星的事了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You heard about Reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-听说了  -我早就料到了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes. - I saw it coming a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,联合国太空指挥部根本不在乎\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}UNSC never gave a shit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,星盟入侵远地殖民地的事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}about the Covenant coming for the Outer Colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这帮人自食其果一点都不奇怪\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I shouldn't be surprised their chickens came home to roost.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:23:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,博得格雷文 在这里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Bodegraven, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.36,0:24:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是他 博得格雷文 男孩 十岁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is him, Bodegraven. Boy, ten years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-是凯斯勒  -好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is Kessler. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你手上这孩子所有资料\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm gonna need everything you got on this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.34,0:24:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.26,0:24:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's timel
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.43,0:24:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.56,0:24:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫不\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What do you mean, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.27,0:24:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他就这么躺被单底下 我们得让他入土为安\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We left him lying under a sheet. We have to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.77,0:24:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-斯巴达战士是不用埋葬的  -行吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You don't bury a Spartan. - Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.61,0:24:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们怎么处理\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So, what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.07,0:24:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-抱歉 帮不了你  -为什么不行\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Sorry, Ican't help you, Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.45,0:24:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你怕了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.71,0:25:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人成为斯巴达战士那一刻起\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The moment a person becomes a Spartan,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.96,0:25:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在你们世界里的生命就终结了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}their life in your world ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.09,0:25:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们生活在我的世界里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They live in mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.96,0:25:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不会被埋葬\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There are no burials.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.63,0:25:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会有葬礼\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There's no funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.59,0:25:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经道过别了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They've already said goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.39,0:25:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太傻了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, that's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.94,0:25:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你会希望能抓住这个机会的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're gonna wish you had taken this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.77,0:25:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道我愿意付出\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You have no idea what I'd give to...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.78,0:25:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这样 去你的吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Know what? Screw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.24,0:25:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己去埋了他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll bury him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.16,0:25:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-没区别  -对我来说有\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It makes no difference. - It does to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.62,0:25:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要把他们埋入地下 留他们在原地\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You put them in the ground and you leave them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.84,0:25:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不然他们会跟着你的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Or they will follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.70,0:26:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我捋一下哈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.70,0:26:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你给清理干净 然后那片土地就是你的了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You gotta clean it up, but then the land is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.04,0:26:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-对 差不多吧  -不错哎 有什么条件吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, pretty much. - Nice. What's the catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.37,0:26:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-没条件  -没条件吗 跟他说呀\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No catch. - No catch? Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.13,0:26:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们不能离开  -永远都不可以吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Not ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.63,0:26:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 但谁会想走呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, but who'd want to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.17,0:26:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I mean, look at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.17,0:26:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你们高兴 很美 对吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm happy for you. It's beautiful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.34,0:26:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-别这样了  -怎么了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Stop. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.22,0:26:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你在交朋友 欣赏风景\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're making friends and enjoying the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.39,0:26:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在找我们的儿子 索伦\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're looking for our son, Soren.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.56,0:26:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.36,0:26:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之前在致远星 这么多人 都死了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We were on Reach. All those people. They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.99,0:26:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,整座城市\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}A whole city.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.24,0:26:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,整个星球\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}A whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.91,0:27:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都不会让你触动吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Does none of that touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.20,0:27:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-当然会了  -那就表现出来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- Of course, it does. - Then act like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.83,0:27:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你想我难过\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You want me to be sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.33,0:27:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.67,0:27:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人往前看\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Somebody's gotta keep looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.75,0:27:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,每次一出天塌了的大事 你永远都不在\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}When things fall apart, you're never there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.38,0:27:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你逃离了斯巴达计划\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You ran from the Spartan program.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.72,0:27:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,从碎石星逃出来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You ran from the Rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.51,0:27:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁比·安找我们的时候 就全靠我一人撑着\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}When Ruby Ann came for us, it was all on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.05,0:27:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Whoa, whoa. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.60,0:27:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这事你不能怪我头上\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You can't blame me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.52,0:27:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在 他们会来对付我们吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Would they have come for us if you'd been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.94,0:27:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实希望你伤心 希望你害怕\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And I do want you to be sad and I do want you to be scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.57,0:27:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我就是这种感觉 我希望你也是一样\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}because that's where I am and I want you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.95,0:27:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你的完美爱人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}♪And your perfect lover ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.96,0:27:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像个十足的傻瓜\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}♪Just looks like A perfect fool ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.21,0:27:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你要逃跑\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}♪ So you go running off♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.59,0:27:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找一个完全陌生的人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}♪In search Of a perfect stranger ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.22,0:28:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而孤独\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}♪While the loneliness ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.80,0:28:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎从你生活中涌出\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}♪ Seems to spring From your life ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.97,0:28:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时就是这个表情\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is exactly how you looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.18,0:28:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我那年14岁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I was 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.52,0:28:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,做完增强手术后醒过来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I woke up after the augmentation and...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.69,0:28:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你看向我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}you looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.19,0:29:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得当时自己说了什么吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you remember what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.19,0:29:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.53,0:29:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,往上看\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.20,0:29:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,三个当中活了一个\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}"One out of three. "
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.83,0:29:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,很多比我强的人都没能活下来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, so many that were better than me didn't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.83,0:29:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中枪\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We get shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.79,0:29:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.21,0:29:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.88,0:29:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,再重来一遍\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We do it all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.34,0:29:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我只会这样\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}That's all I know how to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.34,0:29:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我把一切都教给你了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I taught you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.14,0:29:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,除了如何放弃\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Except how to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.85,0:29:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是为了你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.15,0:29:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.65,0:29:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I did everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.57,0:29:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但伤势太严重了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But the damage is significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.07,0:29:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你没法恢复原来的状态了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You won't be the soldier you once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.41,0:29:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来状态就不比从前\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You were already diminished.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.37,0:29:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.58,0:29:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须更加努力\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}you'll have to work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.29,0:30:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么大只啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Why'd you have to be so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.92,0:30:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,走啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.26,0:30:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样如何\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.31,0:31:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我也是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.82,0:31:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伤害不断累积\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Damage accumulates.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.95,0:31:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她回不去以前的状态了 但时间会帮到她\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She won't be the same as she was, but time will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.24,0:31:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹会活下来 会再次投入战斗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz will live and she will fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.12,0:31:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所有人都不复以往了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, none of us are what we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.63,0:31:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们可有可无\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And now we're expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.17,0:31:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,致远星上发生的事并不是针对个人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What happened on Reach wasn't personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.80,0:31:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至不是策略需要 是政治原因\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It wasn't even strategic. It was political.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.43,0:31:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是巴拉戈斯基\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It was Parangosky.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.85,0:31:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.85,0:31:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,事关控制权\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This was about control.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.64,0:31:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,事关由谁决定这场战争怎么打\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}About who dictates how this war is fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.82,0:31:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她赢了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She won.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.65,0:31:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你没法为整个星球哀悼\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You can't grieve an entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.99,0:31:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太宏大了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.49,0:31:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的思想不会让它成为现实\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Our minds won't let it be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.54,0:32:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这此生命 这些名字\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}AlI those lives. All those names.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.00,0:32:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太多了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.88,0:32:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你帮我做件事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I need you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.17,0:32:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前没机会埋葬别人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I never got to bury anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.68,0:32:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没埋葬过我的人民\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Not my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.72,0:32:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我的家人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Not my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.02,0:32:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不知怎么的 我需要你当所有逝者\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Somehow, I need you to be everyone that's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.23,0:32:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.24,0:32:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,取出科塔娜的人就是巴拉戈斯基\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Parangosky's the one who took Cortana out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.74,0:32:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么可能记得这些\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}How could you possibly have remembered that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.37,0:32:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.25,0:32:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有个空间\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There's a space inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.21,0:32:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那里曾经有个声音\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}where there used to be a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.42,0:32:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得有人认识我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm feeling that somebody knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.92,0:32:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有些东西\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There was something that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.68,0:32:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,科塔娜说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Cortana said.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.43,0:33:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就在她\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}right before she
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.77,0:33:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.02,0:33:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 她说了什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What? What- - What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.19,0:33:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么选的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}How did you choose
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.86,0:33:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}W- W- W- What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.03,0:33:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么选上我的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}How did you choose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.07,0:33:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们创建了基因档案\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We created the genetic profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.95,0:33:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-调查过所有孩子  -不是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We surveyed all the children- - - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.21,0:33:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么选我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.75,0:33:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不明白  -你明白的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't understand. Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.09,0:33:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.10,0:33:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就这一次\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.65,0:33:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还没聊完呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're not done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.99,0:34:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,后退\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.83,0:34:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠近一步 我就拉你们陪葬了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Come closer, I will dig another hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.17,0:34:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-你干什么呢  -嘿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you doing? - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.75,0:34:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这帮疯子要带走他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This crazy's trying to take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.67,0:34:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能把他埋入地下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You can't put him in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.80,0:34:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不同意\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I beg to differ!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.01,0:34:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,把这尸体烧了 让他去找自己的路\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Burn this body. Let him find his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.18,0:34:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-别碰他  -住手\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Get your hands off him! - Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.48,0:34:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.15,0:34:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是死亡\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This isn't death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.12,0:34:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是失去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.45,0:34:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是有区别的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.01,0:34:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,火葬吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Put him in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.73,0:35:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}AlI right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.04,0:35:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-索伦  -在\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.74,0:36:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么事  -晚上好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What do you want? Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.29,0:36:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你这叫非法闯入\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.71,0:36:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-容我解释  -我们是来找儿子的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Allow me to explain. - We're here for our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.04,0:36:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么  -我们的儿子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Your what? - Our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.38,0:36:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.63,0:36:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很听话的小男孩\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.13,0:36:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-差不多这么高  -他是我们的孩子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Like, yay, high- - The kid is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.30,0:36:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼扯\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- The hell he is. -
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.88,0:36:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静一点\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Now...let's calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.76,0:36:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,去别地儿冷静去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You can calm down somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.97,0:36:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个家很好 他喜欢这里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is a good home and he likes it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.77,0:36:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我把他交给了两个陌生人 那我是真该死\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and I'll be damned if I'm giving him up to a couple of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.64,0:36:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是陌生人 我们是他的父母\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're not strangers. We're his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.98,0:36:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是真的 你们也不会是合格的父母\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Even if that were true, some parents you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.57,0:36:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他来到这里时 饿得半死\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He was half starved when he got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.28,0:36:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去还挨了不少揍\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Looked like he'd been slapped around a little too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.82,0:36:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-你说什么  -对\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}- What did you say? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.82,0:36:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我想现在知道罪魁祸首是谁了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I guess we know who's responsible for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.83,0:36:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,草 凯斯勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Fuck you! Kesslerl
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.83,0:36:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒 快出来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kessler, come out here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.46,0:36:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.33,0:36:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在这里 她们带走了他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They have him. They took him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.67,0:37:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 不会有事的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's okay. It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.13,0:37:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-冷静  -我们要怎么办\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Calm down. - What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.30,0:37:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我在呢 我能处理好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm here. I can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.18,0:37:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-不就是场谈判嘛  -这关系到我们的儿子啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's a negotiation. - It's our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.68,0:37:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.35,0:37:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.33,0:37:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你们看上去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, you all seem...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.00,0:37:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,准备充足\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.38,0:37:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不知道世界什么时候会崩塌\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You never know when the world's gonna fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.38,0:37:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.63,0:37:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这茶真不错\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is some really good tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.72,0:37:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我们给你五分钟\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You said to give you five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.81,0:37:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,已经过了两分钟了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We already gave you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.06,0:37:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候生活的地方和这里很像\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I grew up in a place just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.52,0:37:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.19,0:38:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是 我知道勉强维生是什么感觉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It means I know what it is to scratch out a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.40,0:38:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大地产出的粮食总是达不到预期\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The ground never gives you what it promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.53,0:38:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,吃的食物永远不够\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There's never quite enough to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.87,0:38:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们凑合能过\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.70,0:38:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我能搞来东西\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm the kind of guy that can get things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.67,0:38:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,能给予你们补偿的东西\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The kind of things that can compensate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.21,0:38:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道多一双手意味着什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know what an extra pair of hands can mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.11,0:38:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子不卖\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Our boy isn't for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.58,0:39:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,实话和你们说吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm gonna be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.71,0:39:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这里和我长大的地方完全不一样\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is nothing like where I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.59,0:39:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我出生在地狱里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I was born in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.55,0:39:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在拳打脚踢下长大\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Raised in violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.47,0:39:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没有家人 没有家\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Being without a family, without a home...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.48,0:39:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没有食物 没有人保护我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}without food, without protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.94,0:39:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.32,0:39:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.49,0:39:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现 我能挺过这一切\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I realized I can survive all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.75,0:39:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是孤独\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But the loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.79,0:39:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要说什么能要我命\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If anything was gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.84,0:39:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是孤独\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}it would be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.01,0:39:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.34,0:39:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我当父亲了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}So now I'm a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.26,0:39:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我生活在恐惧里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And I live in fear
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:39:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.64,0:40:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我的儿子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}that my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.10,0:40:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,永远体会不到那种感觉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}will never know that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.49,0:40:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,永远体会不到缺少爱是什么感觉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}That absence of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.45,0:40:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,感恩是你们收留了他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I am grateful that you're the ones that took him in,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.54,0:40:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道 他迟早能在这里找到爱\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}because I know in time, he'd find love here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.17,0:40:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但他是我的儿子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But he's my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.48,0:40:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪弄来的这个\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.40,0:40:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一个男孩给我的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}A boy gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.24,0:40:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在运输飞船上\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}On the transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.74,0:40:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,用来保护自己的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}For protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.08,0:41:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他发现我害怕\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He- - He saw that I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.00,0:41:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.25,0:41:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,被他们带走了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They took him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.26,0:41:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她们愿意让我们见凯斯勒了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They're gonna let us see Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.10,0:41:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.90,0:41:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不是凯斯勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.97,0:42:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,致远星不仅是一个地方\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Reach was more than a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.31,0:42:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,更是一个象征\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It was a symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.97,0:42:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是人类精神的丰碑\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It was a monument to the human spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.81,0:42:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,纪念着牺牲了一切保卫这里的人们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and to those who sacrificed everything to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.44,0:42:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,比如雅各布·凯斯上将\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Those like Admiral Jacob Keyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.99,0:42:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,以及这位斯巴达战士 瓦纳克·阿马迪\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And this Spartan, Vannak Amadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.33,0:42:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他在致敬星上出生\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He was born on Tribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.00,0:42:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识他时他才六岁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I met him when he was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.79,0:42:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看得出来 他很有荣誉感\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I could see he had honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.50,0:42:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他生活在大家族里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He had a large family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.17,0:42:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他尽忠效劳 他的家人会为他骄傲的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They would be proud of his service.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.98,0:42:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他的家人在他六岁时就埋葬了他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}His family buried him when he was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.81,0:42:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从来不了解他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They never knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.53,0:42:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但我了解\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.54,0:43:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字是瓦纳克-134\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}His name was Vannak- 134.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.21,0:43:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个斯巴达战士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He was a Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.55,0:43:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们的兄弟\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He was our brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.18,0:43:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是自己认识的唯一的亲人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And the only family that he ever knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.39,0:43:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他这一生并不平凡\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This...This was not an ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.35,0:43:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他做过的一切 付出的一切\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Everything that he was, everything that he gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.24,0:43:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,永垂不朽\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}it never dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.09,0:43:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你的战斗没有结束\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Your fight is not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.67,0:44:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我会成为你的武器\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I will be your weapon now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.55,0:44:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找到害死你的人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I will find the ones who caused your death,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.22,0:44:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要了他们的命\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}and I will end them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.66,0:45:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你能接近巴拉戈斯基\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You think you can get to Parangosky?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.42,0:45:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,接近艾克森吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}To Ackerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.62,0:45:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你连他们在哪里都不知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You don't even know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.17,0:45:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找到他们的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.50,0:45:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你只会害死你自己\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're gonna get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.34,0:45:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有选择你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I didn't choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.43,0:45:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.35,0:45:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么东西打造了光环\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Whatever built the Halo,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.85,0:45:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么东西留下了那些制品\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}whatever left those artifacts behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.65,0:45:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它们也在你的内心留下了点什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}left something in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.48,0:45:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你逃避不了的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You can't run from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.86,0:45:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你一辈子的召唤\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This has been calling to you your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.70,0:45:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你注定要完成的使命\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is what you're meant to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.62,0:45:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在只有一件事情要做 那就是找到巴拉戈斯基和艾克森\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The only thing I have to do is find Parangosky, Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.54,0:45:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰 你能带我们去光环\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}John, you can take us to the Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.96,0:46:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们种族能不能活下来 就看光环能教会我们什么了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The survival of our species depends on what it can teach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.30,0:46:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你自己去找海军情报局报仇 那就是让我们所有人陪你冒险\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If you go after ONI yourself, you put all of that at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.34,0:46:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会给你留生路的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They can't let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.35,0:46:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经死了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.74,0:46:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,加入我们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.24,0:46:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.75,0:46:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Sorry, did
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.42,0:46:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才和我说了什么吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Did you say something to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.21,0:46:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表星球说话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I speak for the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.43,0:46:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.09,0:46:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表所有星球说话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I speak for all the planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.02,0:46:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.73,0:47:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,人都去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.94,0:47:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表牧歌星说话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I speak for Madrigal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.86,0:47:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.36,0:47:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我痛苦地呐喊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I cry out in painl
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.78,0:47:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子灰飞烟灭\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}My children are ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.79,0:47:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的皮肤破裂 我的心\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}My skin is broken. My heart- -
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.75,0:47:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是谁啊  -你是谁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Who the hell are you? - Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.92,0:47:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谁也不是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.59,0:47:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你是关哈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're Kwan Ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.80,0:47:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哈氏一族最后一人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Last of the Has.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.27,0:47:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}How do you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.64,0:47:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是谁  -你背叛了我们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Who are you? - You turned your back on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.15,0:47:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-你忘记了自己的姓名  -别过来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You forgot your name. - Get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.65,0:47:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.48,0:47:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-怪物  -你别过来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The monster. Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.65,0:47:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助我 找到我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Help me. Find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.82,0:47:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救我 解救我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Deliver me. Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.62,0:47:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要否认你的使命\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do not deny your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.16,0:47:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要抛弃你的姓名  -别说了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do not forsake your name. - Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.95,0:47:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,守护者\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.13,0:48:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.29,0:48:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.96,0:48:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么在博爱城\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Why are we at High Charity?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.63,0:48:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的舰队被召回了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Our fleet has been recalled.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.43,0:48:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们有任务 要去找回\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}No. We have a mission, to retrieve the--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.97,0:48:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务失败了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We failed the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.64,0:48:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.21,0:49:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他们会怎么对我们吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you know what they will do to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.94,0:49:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么对我吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}To me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.45,0:49:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能希望 他们会接受这个信物\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I can only hope that they will accept this token as an offering,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.95,0:49:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为我失败的补偿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}to mitigate my failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.92,0:49:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么做\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do not do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.66,0:49:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高等先知已经下令了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The Hierarchs command it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.86,0:49:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高等先知是骗子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The Hierarchs are liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.66,0:49:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再辱骂一句 我就撕碎你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Blaspheme again, and I will rip the breath from your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.23,0:49:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先知满嘴谎言\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The Prophets are false.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.94,0:49:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本没想着开启朝圣之旅\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They have no intention of beginning the Great Journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.00,0:49:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有能力这么做\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It is not in their power to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.54,0:49:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们非天选之人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They are not Chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.24,0:49:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们心知肚明 这是我们的命运 我看见了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And they know it. It is our destiny I have seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.48,0:49:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能带领我们前往圣迹环带\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You will be the one to lead us to the Sacred Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.41,0:49:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拍的马屁既残忍又空洞\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Your flattery is as cruel as it is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.95,0:49:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些先知让你为此感到羞愧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}These Prophets that would shame you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.15,0:49:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们惧怕你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}do so because they fear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.79,0:49:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们看到了你的伟大和你纯粹的信念\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They see your greatness and the purity of your faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.39,0:49:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们因自己的虚伪而窒息\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And it makes them choke on their hypocrisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.40,0:50:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么做到的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}How are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.74,0:50:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 是你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is not my doing. This is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.18,0:50:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的命运 你只要接受就好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}This is your destiny. You need only take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.02,0:50:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么做\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What must I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.95,0:50:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信 你要相信 相信我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Believe. You must believe. In me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.32,0:50:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是世尊者\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I am the Blessed One.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.36,0:51:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会派出一整支舰队来追捕我们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}They will send the entire fleet to hunt us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.66,0:51:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会失败的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And they will fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.84,0:51:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切早已命中注定\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It is written.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.28,0:52:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.70,0:52:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有手套吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.78,0:52:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那边\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.63,0:52:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.63,0:53:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样我没认出来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I didn't recognize you with your
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.92,0:53:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有带刺铁丝网吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you have any barbed wire?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.80,0:53:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个和你一起的家伙呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's that, uh, fella that was with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.14,0:53:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他想来的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He wanted to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.81,0:53:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得这样不太慎重\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But I didn't think that would be prudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.65,0:53:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,慎重\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Prudent?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.77,0:53:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他有点情绪化\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He can be a bit emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.95,0:53:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情况我看得更明白\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Whereas I see this kind of situation a bit more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.83,0:53:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-我没明白  -你肯定明白\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't think I understand. - Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.25,0:53:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前有过妈妈 对吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You had a mother, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.08,0:53:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-对  -没有人应该挡在\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah. - No one should come
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.00,0:53:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈和孩子之间\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}between a mother and her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.00,0:53:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这个纽带很强大\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's a powerful bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.01,0:53:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,天生的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Instinctive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.67,0:53:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这里来过很多孩子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You know, we got a lot of kids coming through here- -
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.47,0:53:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,几天前\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.52,0:53:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我在空气里闻到了一丝气味 让我回到了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I caught a scent in the air, that took me back
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.86,0:54:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次给凯斯勒剪头发的时候\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}to the first time I cut Kessler's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.69,0:54:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他那时还那么小\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He was so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.15,0:54:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,女士 我就是个开店的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Look, lady, I- I'm just a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.32,0:54:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他扭来扭去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}He was squirming.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.16,0:54:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心会划伤他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I was nervous that I would hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.16,0:54:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候我就知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And that's when I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.87,0:54:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果谁伤害了他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}that if anyone ever caused him pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.38,0:54:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道自己会做出什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}there's no telling what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.96,0:54:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不惜一切\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}There would be no limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.89,0:54:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的意思吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.24,0:54:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他说了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Did he talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.69,0:54:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,说了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.70,0:54:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他说了凯斯勒是被谁带走的吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Did he say who took Kessler?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.53,0:54:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,联合国太空指挥部\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}The UNSC.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.38,0:55:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,十分钟后出发\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We're wheels up in ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.06,0:55:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.60,0:55:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-收拾一下  -我做不到了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}get your stuff- - - I'm not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.94,0:55:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.11,0:55:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没事的  -我要留在这里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're gonna be fine. I'm gonna stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.11,0:55:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,集中注意力打仗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Get your head in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.78,0:55:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的战争结束了 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}My fight's over, Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.20,0:55:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦纳克说结束时才结束\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's over when Vannak says it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.29,0:55:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-凯说  -士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}When Kai says- - Chief
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.46,0:55:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,赢了才算结束\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}It's over when we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.46,0:55:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}On your feet
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.30,0:55:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我命令你 斯巴达战士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I gave you an order, Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.55,0:55:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.45,0:56:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去了致远星\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We lost Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.28,0:56:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去了瓦纳克\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We lost Vannak
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.45,0:56:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-凯  -我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Kai- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.79,0:56:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你打算怎么做\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Then what are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.75,0:56:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要活下去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm going to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.96,0:56:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你没资格说不\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You don't get to say no to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.30,0:56:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们欠他们的 里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We owe them, Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.68,0:56:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去了他们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}We lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.35,0:56:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-我失去了他们  -只是痛苦而已\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I lost them. It's just pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.81,0:56:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做的只有带着痛苦前行\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}All you can do is carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.02,0:56:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它很沉重\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}But it's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.15,0:56:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但你越不愿面对 越逃避\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}And the more you deny it, the more you run from it,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.02,0:56:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它就会变得越沉重\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}the heavier it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.11,0:56:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不和痛苦和解 你会被压垮的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}If you don't make peace with it, it will crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.03,0:56:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让痛苦压垮我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I won't let it crush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.62,0:57:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有你了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}You're all I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.17,0:57:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.90,0:57:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她不来了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}She's not coming
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.20,0:57:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在谁也不是了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}you're no one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.34,0:59:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,全体都有\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}Attention on deck!


